Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.02,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:22.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.50,Adachi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节和岛村一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:33.98,Adachi,,0,0,0,,会不会很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.17,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就算是模拟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,总是想起奇怪的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:44.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,最近体育馆二楼变冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,也不怎么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.64,Adachi,,0,0,0,,想见岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:53.08,Adachi,,0,0,0,,想和岛村二人度过的特别时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:58.29,Adachi,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话 我想是圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:03.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,问题是 特意的约在圣诞节那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:12.07,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是不是笔压得太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.95,Adachi,,0,0,0,,即使擦掉还是有名字留在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:18.90,Adachi,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛睡觉 即使到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,也忘不了昨天的岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:22.93,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那点有些相似
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.34,Adachi,,0,0,0,,如果我被岛村提出要求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,到哪种程度才会接受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.45,Adachi,,0,0,0,,帮我拿下书包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:08.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不 不是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.90,Adachi,,0,0,0,,抱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.31,Adachi,,0,0,0,,努力？ 大概会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.94,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一起睡午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:24.27,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:27.71,Adachi,,0,0,0,,太过于想着在圣诞节约岛村出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.07,Adachi,,0,0,0,,像是在边缘爬上树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.98,Adachi,,0,0,0,,然后就这样下不了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.82,Adachi,,0,0,0,,呀呀 岛村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.38,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.43,Adachi,,0,0,0,,没什么 没有事就不能找你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.14,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:56.42,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.55,Adachi,,0,0,0,,喔 安达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.57,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有学习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.51,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.40,Adachi,,0,0,0,,诶 有什么学习啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.25,Adachi,,0,0,0,,挺认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.04,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊这..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.45,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,今天去永藤家玩吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:17.50,Adachi,,0,0,0,,总感觉每天都能在被炉旁看见你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.02,Adachi,,0,0,0,,错觉 错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:26.57,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.40,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不对 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.35,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 反省
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.07,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯~ 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我说点什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:37.78,Adachi,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.03,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你问我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:43.06,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这当作今后的课题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.14,Adachi,,0,0,0,,然后 安达有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.24,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊 那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.86,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:54.37,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,学习 之类..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.22,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那么 和日野她们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.06,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不是  那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但是 她们比我们成绩好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:09.95,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就算成绩很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:13.52,Adachi,,0,0,0,,跟我们一起学习他们也没有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:14.84,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:21.69,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达居然把我想成我们成绩都差不多的笨蛋吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.17,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:27.99,Adachi,,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.13,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那 就两个一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.99,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要去哪里 图书馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:35.14,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还是说家庭餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.03,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.31,Adachi,,0,0,0,,家 岛村的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.32,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.93,Adachi,,0,0,0,,诶~ 都是灰尘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:45.78,Adachi,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达的家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.65,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我家 有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.40,Adachi,,0,0,0,,难道说我也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.28,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:58.26,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那去我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.22,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但是有很多灰尘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.06,Adachi,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.77,Adachi,,0,0,0,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.50,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.81,Adachi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:14.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你朋友？喔 house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.47,Adachi,,0,0,0,,额 喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.72,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你是安达酱对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:19.60,Adachi,,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:20.96,Adachi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,去房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,房间不是在那边...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.39,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.02,Adachi,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,学习房间在二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.92,Adachi,,0,0,0,,哪个都不显眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.79,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你可真会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:51.52,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.71,Adachi,,0,0,0,,永藤肉店的新吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,可乐饼酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:00.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.04,Adachi,,0,0,0,,什么就用这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.38,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还擅自取名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.62,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那给日野奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:09.99,Adachi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.50,Adachi,,0,0,0,,难道又是亲额头？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.17,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.62,Adachi,,0,0,0,,算了 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:36.84,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你们真的很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:41.46,Adachi,,0,0,0,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.66,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要吃橘子的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:48.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我们算很要好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,很普通吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.61,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 很普通的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.35,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:04.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,呐 我说过有很多灰尘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.86,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这就是学习的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:12.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,总之在变暖之前先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.80,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达是在学习的时候喜欢听音乐的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:19.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 经常听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.41,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.66,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:25.60,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,圣 圣...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.71,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村小时候是什么样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.58,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 很普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好像一直在当配餐委員...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:44.80,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊 头发比现在还短吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.28,Adachi,,0,0,0,,也没有染发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:51.15,Adachi,,0,0,0,,短发的岛村 还有黑发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.19,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.25,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达呢? 小时候是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.41,Adachi,,0,0,0,,额  那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.07,Adachi,,0,0,0,,和现在一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.68,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯~ 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.81,Adachi,,0,0,0,,以前都是让保育士牵着手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.89,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.94,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.35,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就是..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有好好挑选对象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:23.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.78,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样不是在像告白一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.62,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯~ 为什么是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.90,Adachi,,0,0,0,,刚才..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.19,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村说了 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.53,Adachi,,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个问题很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.71,Adachi,,0,0,0,,因为是岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样回答的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:12.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就完全明显的表达自己很喜欢岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:14.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不行不行 冷靜下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:29.57,Adachi,,0,0,0,,在亲的时候醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那就真的完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:37.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,而且 我也不是一定要亲岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:42.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村要求的话才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.31,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不是那样的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.30,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.60,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.25,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这边比较软 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是这样啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.03,Adachi,,0,0,0,,很想睡觉啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.84,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不睡唷~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:19.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,给 很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.84,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊... 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,呐 岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:27.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.88,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村你 额..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,圣..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.39,Adachi,,0,0,0,,圣诞节是怎么过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,晚饭有炸鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.04,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还有蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.36,Adachi,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,50)}不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.35,Adachi,,0,0,0,,妹妹还相信有圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:51.32,Adachi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.12,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村到几岁还信着？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.52,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.42,Adachi,,0,0,0,,没有相信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.96,Adachi,,0,0,0,,正常来说没有这么好的大叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.22,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我一直以为是保育园的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.14,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:13.81,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我想只有保育园的大人有说过圣诞老人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:17.30,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我们都是不称职的小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.31,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,小时候比现在更傻更奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:26.68,Adachi,,0,0,0,,居然有办法活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.41,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那时不会有腰酸背痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:41.90,Adachi,,0,0,0,,现在就想像这样和岛村在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.51,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就像用翅膀保护心爱的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:47.88,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就这样持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,最近 安达的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.27,Adachi,,0,0,0,,首先是看过来的视线变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.37,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那是奇怪的第一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.69,Adachi,,0,0,0,,第二点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:05.52,Adachi,,0,0,0,,说话的时候感觉忍耐着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.68,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嘴唇不会肌肉痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:11.95,Adachi,,0,0,0,,第三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.60,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.58,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.41,Adachi,,0,0,0,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:26.08,Adachi,,0,0,0,,英语成绩比我还好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.98,Adachi,,0,0,0,,第三到没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.83,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,疼......
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.02,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.35,Adachi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.91,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.48,Adachi,,0,0,0,,试着玩一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:52.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,先不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.89,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个... 岛村？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.42,Adachi,,0,0,0,,来 深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,很好 唷 安达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.49,Adachi,,0,0,0,,希望安达能正常的打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.43,Adachi,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.42,Adachi,,0,0,0,,大概不会有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.36,Adachi,,0,0,0,,然后 最近怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:26.88,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你指的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.91,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你总是在看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.96,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.23,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有什么事想跟我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:38.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.43,0:14:41.55,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 那说来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:46.37,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个..冬天还是下周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.95,Adachi,,0,0,0,,大概10天后？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:49.97,Adachi,,0,0,0,,10天后？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,等我再有一点胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.69,Adachi,,0,0,0,,考虑一下告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.77,Adachi,,0,0,0,,在幼儿园有个特别好要的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:11.43,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一直都藏在我身后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.82,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一句话来说就是很像安达的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那时我还毫无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.59,Adachi,,0,0,0,,对任何事物都感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,她总跟着我的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:27.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,她喜欢弹珠和风铃那种亮晶晶的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.98,Adachi,,0,0,0,,只有找到这个东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:34.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,从我身后离开 跑到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,大家请看今天在sns非常的火的一张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.27,Adachi,,0,0,0,,装食物的袋子拿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.17,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:52.96,Adachi,,0,0,0,,姐姐也快点去学校哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.64,Adachi,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:59.51,Adachi,,0,0,0,,高中生只有在太阳完全升起之前到学校就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.39,Adachi,,0,0,0,,谁教的 这傻规则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:03.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,快点吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.48,Adachi,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,姐姐的朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.40,Adachi,,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,哈？ 朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.43,Adachi,,0,0,0,,之前来的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.19,Adachi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.89,Adachi,,0,0,0,,呀 呀 安达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.28,Adachi,,0,0,0,,早好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.89,Adachi,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.44,Adachi,,0,0,0,,为什么是假装体育系？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,话说会不会太早了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊？ 你几时来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,有点事想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.22,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我觉得这时间很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.44,Adachi,,0,0,0,,刚来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:13.65,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.53,Adachi,,0,0,0,,很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.51,Adachi,,0,0,0,,外面这冷 进来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.26,Adachi,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.03,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.23,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达酱帮她吃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.78,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我家孩子吃得很慢 很烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不用说多余的话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.21,Adachi,,0,0,0,,那个...我在家里吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.58,Adachi,,0,0,0,,吃了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.90,Adachi,,0,0,0,,一个面包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.78,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你母亲不会说再多吃吃点嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.46,Adachi,,0,0,0,,够了~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.26,Adachi,,0,0,0,,父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.91,Adachi,,0,0,0,,比起女儿在意腰围吃得少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:55.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,稍微胖一下比较安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.23,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不会这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.22,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不常跟我说话 也不常在家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好~ 去房间里聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我把暖气打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.53,Adachi,,0,0,0,,你就在那边随便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.62,Adachi,,0,0,0,,所以 要说的话是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.72,Adachi,,0,0,0,,昨天也问了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.72,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,emmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.75,Adachi,,0,0,0,,岛村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.24,Adachi,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要不要去哪玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.18,Adachi,,0,0,0,,之类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.37,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.04,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就这？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.33,Adachi,,0,0,0,,可以啊 放学后？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.96,Adachi,,0,0,0,,难道现在就不去学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.40,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊...不是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.82,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:07.70,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这个月的25号怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,25？ 25号啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.63,Adachi,,0,0,0,,12月的25号是....  啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.44,Adachi,,0,0,0,,25号是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.48,Adachi,,0,0,0,,是圣诞节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.10,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.39,Adachi,,0,0,0,,为什么想说为什么但没说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.05,Adachi,,0,0,0,,为什么是圣诞节 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:40.72,Adachi,,0,0,0,,感觉我问了为什么 我们关系的骨干就瘫软扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:45.73,Adachi,,0,0,0,,想要治疗 就要付出巨大努力和劳动力时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,我这样一想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,就是马上看见冰冷的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:55.50,Adachi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.42,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:02.68,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还没有想好去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:04.98,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.28,Adachi,,0,0,0,,还没有想好做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.64,Adachi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:16.38,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达在家里 感受不到圣诞节的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.30,Adachi,,0,0,0,,才拜托我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.80,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样的话我也能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.84,Adachi,,0,0,0,,无论是态度和通红的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.64,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这完全是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:29.68,Adachi,,0,0,0,,和告白一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.44,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊 没有特别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.65,Adachi,,0,0,0,,说到圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:40.00,Adachi,,0,0,0,,在这热闹的日子和谁一起玩之类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.74,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不对 想试试过下这样的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.29,Adachi,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.11,Adachi,,0,0,0,,和谁一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:54.08,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但是没有别的朋友 只能找到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:57.36,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不是想和我 和谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:01.31,Adachi,,0,0,0,,这样啊 这样的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:06.24,Adachi,,0,0,0,,只要在吃饭前回来 之前都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:07.79,Adachi,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:11.57,Adachi,,0,0,0,,但去哪里都要安达考虑好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.85,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.16,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达犬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.15,Adachi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.69,Adachi,,0,0,0,,要赶快去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:43.04,Adachi,,0,0,0,,嗯 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.55,Adachi,,0,0,0,,哦 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不快点的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.09,Adachi,,0,0,0,,啊 快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.82,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.93,Adachi,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.67,Adachi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.81,Adachi,,0,0,0,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.66,Adachi,,0,0,0,,为什么像时代剧那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:09.14,Adachi,,0,0,0,,也让我搭下车哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:13.28,Adachi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:20.03,Adachi,,0,0,0,,总之 今年的圣诞节决定和安达一起出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:25.34,Adachi,,0,0,0,,反正在家圣诞老人也不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:26.99,Adachi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1512,926)}第5话  安达Q
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:00.87,Adachi,,0,0,0,,安达岛村百科 被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:00.87,Adachi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1397.333,921.334)}下回 「白色相簿」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:02.87,Adachi,,0,0,0,,人进了被炉就不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:04.54,Adachi,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:05.94,Adachi,,0,0,0,,倒杯茶~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.57,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不要 不想动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:08.69,Adachi,,0,0,0,,预告~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:09.97,Adachi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:11.20,Adachi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.88,Adachi,,0,0,0,,真不错 真不错
